{"tid":350782,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老母患上糖尿病，冇經驗，可以教佢食啲乜？","createTime":"2017-08-07T13:29:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T05:13:12.000Z","uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c714c33c5c8ca542d1703294bb424618a52e08b","tid":350782,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T13:29:33.000Z","msg":"好似話連飯都唔好食咁多，碳水化合物太高，食麵係咪好啲？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪蔬菜一定冇鑊氣？瓜類豆類呢？<br />\n<br />\n太多嘢要注意，一時間千頭萬緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8040e5a88fcdee1fa1d1a836a9c2e04eb9c65a2a","tid":350782,"uid":17677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T14:08:28.000Z","msg":"多菜 食多d南瓜 魚<br />\n飯就小小 唔好太多<br />\n但點都要食 <br />\n水果就睇下邊d 太甜都唔好<br />\n做d伸展運動都有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbce6641a701bc11c2c6240ef39024bb72c8a249","tid":350782,"uid":17677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T14:11:18.000Z","msg":"麵就好小小 但小心針份量"},{"pid":"42904ecd2422c4a3fe413771c894a355a243eae4","tid":350782,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T14:30:57.000Z","msg":"Google diabetes food list<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://www.webmd.com/diabetes/diabetic-food-list-best-worst-foods&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiP7IX0qsXVAhXBp5QKHVFxAFMQFgg6MAM&amp;usg=AFQjCNEt-IceD83YC1LfgkqYvoqzXpN2vw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.webmd.com%2Fdiabetes%2Fdiabetic-food-list-best-worst-foods%26ved%3D0ahUKEwiP7IX0qsXVAhXBp5QKHVFxAFMQFgg6MAM%26usg%3DAFQjCNEt-IceD83YC1LfgkqYvoqzXpN2vw&d=lh8eEwqKkF3ilPH2M05HX0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=d62da9f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://www.webmd.com/diabetes/diabetic-food-list-best-worst-foods&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiP7IX0qsXVAhXBp5QKHVFxAFMQFgg6MAM&amp;usg=AFQjCNEt-IceD83YC1LfgkqYvoqzXpN2vw</a>"},{"pid":"05779c4c27a955790ff96cf616423dfa50ea3996","tid":350782,"uid":9387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T15:14:08.000Z","msg":"多數麵米粉通粉都係精製 唔會好過白飯<br />\n可以食麥皮 唔好即溶果隻 愈原始愈好<br />\n或者糙米飯 全麥pasta <br />\n避免飲甜野"},{"pid":"6c0274843d700cdb408d7a2145b21df36680a40a","tid":350782,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:25:26.000Z","msg":"買本糖尿飲食既書吧"},{"pid":"ea438e4b8d3266eafbbc97da3b15a709eea7ab47","tid":350782,"uid":118130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:25:39.000Z","msg":"小食多餐。有冇食藥？記得唔好唔食嘢，做吓啲運動，隨身帶定啲糖免得血糖低，小心唔好咁易整親撞親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">利申:小學護</span></span>"},{"pid":"011333048484ab2d3fe02faa832da3e144009dd1","tid":350782,"uid":45821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:27:22.000Z","msg":"糖尿病係無得斷尾？"},{"pid":"b7cbb66705369008b9cd28ce1b0b7781518b7527","tid":350782,"uid":37267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:29:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>糖尿病係無得斷尾？</blockquote><br />\n後天個隻靠運動+飲食係可以整返好"},{"pid":"3ed70663eea8afea5f3b00c9c934890bfb019184","tid":350782,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:49:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"615cd7e9c5fd15a4008de2ebfb384cd60e79fbfe","tid":350782,"uid":53421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:52:14.000Z","msg":"去力威醫"},{"pid":"aedf93929c585f4b1414909d2376a7cc137055c1","tid":350782,"uid":20134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:55:03.000Z","msg":"食中藥"},{"pid":"fc6603471b98d08f6f2500fb4f6a0962732211a4","tid":350782,"uid":50144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:13:12.000Z","msg":"一定食飯嘅話，溝米嚟食。紅黑糙小米同藜麥都可以考慮。"}]}